  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">It&apos;s a matter of heart.  Thousands of children in the world suffer from congenital heart disease, which will certainly bring them to death, if we do not intervene as soon as possible.  Join us, Give the Beat, and help us save the heart of so many children!  The average cost of a heart operation of a baby, in the countries where we intervene, is about 1500 USD. What are you waiting for? Help us too! Even with a small contribution, we can do so much.</narrative>
